v2.1.2
======
We have split the package from 'chleb-bible-search' into three packages:

  * chleb-bible-search: meta-package
  * chleb-bible-search-core: The code
  * chleb-bible-search-dict: Dictionaries

In the future, optional dictionary files will be supplied in one or more additional, separate .deb files

We have made significant changes to the logrotate config so it merely compresses, but Log4Perl rotates.
